<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17253949295380538965">Matthew Walker is a British scientist and professor of neuroscience and psychology at the University of California, Berkeley. His research focuses on the impact of sleep on human health and disease. Previously, he was a professor of psychiatry at Harvard Medical School.</span>

